---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 所有標籤
permalink: /tags/
description: 瀏覽 FW Blog 的所有文章標籤與相關文章數量。
---

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">所有標籤</h1>

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
{% for tag in collections.tagList %}
  {% set tagPosts = collections.posts | filterByTag(tag) %}
  <a href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/"
     class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-200 transition">
    #{{ tag }} <span class="text-blue-600">({{ tagPosts.length }})</span>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</div>

{% if collections.tagList.length == 0 %}
<p class="text-gray-600">目前還沒有任何標籤。</p>
{% endif %}
